            <title>[CASSANDRA-20686] Accord: startup race condition where accord journal tries to access the 2i index before its ready</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20686</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a short race condition issue where accord tries to access the journal 2i before its ready (setup is asynchronous, even if there is no work to do); this causes the main process to crash!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
